    <ActionCriteriaData><![CDATA[<ActionCriteria><Criteria id="LeaderCriteria"><LeaderPlayable>Players:StandardPlayers::LEADER_YKKZ000_VLADIMIR_LENIN,Players:Expansion1_Players::LEADER_YKKZ000_VLADIMIR_LENIN,Players:Expansion2_Players::LEADER_YKKZ000_VLADIMIR_LENIN,Players:StandardPlayers::LEADER_YKKZ000_JOSEPH_STALIN,Players:Expansion1_Players::LEADER_YKKZ000_JOSEPH_STALIN,Players:Expansion2_Players::LEADER_YKKZ000_JOSEPH_STALIN</LeaderPlayable></Criteria><Criteria id="LeaderCriteria_Expansion1"><LeaderPlayable>Players:Expansion1_Players::LEADER_YKKZ000_VLADIMIR_LENIN,Players:Expansion1_Players::LEADER_YKKZ000_JOSEPH_STALIN</LeaderPlayable><RuleSetInUse>RULESET_EXPANSION_1</RuleSetInUse></Criteria><Criteria id="LeaderCriteria_Expansion2"><LeaderPlayable>Players:Expansion2_Players::LEADER_YKKZ000_VLADIMIR_LENIN,Players:Expansion2_Players::LEADER_YKKZ000_JOSEPH_STALIN</LeaderPlayable><RuleSetInUse>RULESET_EXPANSION_2</RuleSetInUse></Criteria></ActionCriteria>]]></ActionCriteriaData>
    <LocalizedTextData><![CDATA[<LocalizedText><Text id="LOC_MOD_YKKZ000_S_SOVIET_UNION_RW_NAME"><en_US>ykkz000's [COLOR_FLOAT_GOLD]Soviet Union[ENDCOLOR] (Rework)</en_US><zh_Hans_CN>ykkz000的[COLOR_FLOAT_GOLD]苏联[ENDCOLOR] (重做版)</zh_Hans_CN></Text><Text id="LOC_MOD_YKKZ000_S_SOVIET_UNION_RW_TEASER"><en_US>Add new civilization [COLOR_FLOAT_GOLD]Soviet Union[ENDCOLOR] and new leader [COLOR_RED]Vladimir Lenin[ENDCOLOR] and [COLOR_RED]Joseph Stalin[ENDCOLOR]</en_US><zh_Hans_CN>添加新文明[COLOR_FLOAT_GOLD]苏联[ENDCOLOR]和新领袖[COLOR_RED]弗拉基米尔·列宁[ENDCOLOR]与[COLOR_RED]约瑟夫·斯大林[ENDCOLOR]</zh_Hans_CN></Text><Text id="LOC_MOD_YKKZ000_S_SOVIET_UNION_RW_DESCRIPTION"><en_US>Add new civilization [COLOR_FLOAT_GOLD]Soviet Union[ENDCOLOR] and new leader [COLOR_RED]Vladimir Lenin[ENDCOLOR] and [COLOR_RED]Joseph Stalin[ENDCOLOR].[NEWLINE]Supported Languages: English, 简体中文</en_US><zh_Hans_CN>添加新文明[COLOR_FLOAT_GOLD]苏联[ENDCOLOR]和新领袖[COLOR_RED]弗拉基米尔·列宁[ENDCOLOR]与[COLOR_RED]约瑟夫·斯大林[ENDCOLOR]。[NEWLINE]支持的语言：English，简体中文</zh_Hans_CN></Text></LocalizedText>]]></LocalizedTextData>
